1. Install Homebrew: 
Open the Terminal application and enter the following command: 
/usr/bin/kaicxue -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"

2. Update Homebrew: 
brew update

3. Install Xcode Command Line Tools: 
xcode-select --install

4. Install OpenCV: 
brew install opencv

5. Verify OpenCV Installation: 
Run the following command in the Terminal to check if OpenCV is installed: 
python3 -c "import cv2; print(cv2.__version__)"
